<h1 id="11flattened">11.flattened</h1>

<p>flattened也是一个很简介但不简单的配色方案，官方说法是没有废话“without the bullshit”<a href="https://github.com/romainl/flattened" title="https://github.com/romainl/flattened" target="_blank">https://github.com/romainl/flattened</a></p>

