<h1 id="12railscasts">12.railscasts</h1>

<p>railscasts同时支持GUI和终端方式，github地址为：<a href="https://github.com/jpo/vim-railscasts-theme" title="https://github.com/jpo/vim-railscasts-theme" target="_blank">https://github.com/jpo/vim-railscasts-theme</a></p>

