<h1 id="13seoul256">13.seoul256</h1>

<p>seoul256是一个低对比度(low-contrast)的配色方案，github地址：<a href="https://github.com/junegunn/seoul256.vim" title="https://github.com/junegunn/seoul256.vim" target="_blank">https://github.com/junegunn/seoul256.vim</a></p>

